===Alley Dwellers===  

*Constantly talk to themselves, proposing nonsense.
*Not interested in trading for resources.
*Locations constantly change within the bounds of the level.
*Very hostile towards wanderers who enter this level.

Due to fresh food only appearing when out of sight and the average portion of said food being enough for only one person, a large-scale, stationary settlement within '''Level 877''' is currently infeasible.

