*Finding the corresponding level door's key in [[The Hub]] and unlocking it leads to this level.
*Eating a bowl of stir-fried noodles in [[Level 610]] may lead you to this level.
*Entering a dimly lit alley in [[Level 11]] leads here.
*Noclipping through a shop gate in [[Level 859]] can lead here. 

